</XX>
<CO>Sidlaw Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2281 Yarn Spinning Mills.
    P1389 Oil and Gas Field Services, NEC.
</IN>
