<HEADLINE>
FT  15 NOV 93 / People: Pentland
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Peter McGuigan, chief executive of Speedo who also has responsibility for
Berghaus, has been appointed to the main board of PENTLAND with worldwide
responsibility for the branded sporting goods businesses.
</TEXT>
